item.title: CVE-2019-18374|2024-08-05T01:54:14.052Z -- symantec -- critical%20system%20protection%20%28csp%29
item.description: Symantec Critical System Protection (CSP), versions 8.0, 8.0 HF1 & 8.0 MP1, may be susceptible to an authentication bypass vulnerability, which is a type of issue that can potentially allow a threat actor to circumvent existing authentication controls.
